  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bb3\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u2013 \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Countries with high debt and limited policies risk crisis like Sri Lanka - IMF",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "International Monetary Fund Managing Director Kristalina Georgieva said Sri Lanka is a warning sign for countries with huge debt and restrictive policies.",
        "He said this at the meeting of G20 finance ministers and central bank governors held in Indonesia.",
        "The war in Ukraine has escalated due to which the prices of essential commodities, including foodstuffs, have increased, the international financial situation has become tighter than expected, the confusion related to the pandemic and the obstacles facing international distribution are affecting economic activity, he said.",
        "At the end of this month, we estimate that economic growth for 2022-23 will decline, and downside risks will be severe, particularly higher inflation, he said.",
        "He also mentioned that countries with high debt and restrictive policies may face further pressures. Look at the direction Sri Lanka is going."
      ],
